title: [Rocky Shore, Boulder Field]
description: You are in a narrow gap between the massive boulder and the cliffside.  The breeze is totally absent and despite the cool rock surface, you are sweating in the stagnant night air.  The rocks here are slippery with accumulated droppings from the nests of birds high above you in the broken clefts of the upper cliffs.
